.Li false ) .
Mutually exclusive with
.Ar data_only .
.It Ar data_only
Dump only the data, no schema (default:
.Li false ) .
Mutually exclusive with
.Ar schema_only .
.It Ar pg_dump
Path to the
.Xr pg_dump 1
binary (default:
.Li pg_dump ) .
.It Ar pg_dumpall
Path to the
.Xr pg_dumpall 1
binary (default:
.Li pg_dumpall ) .
.It Ar psql
Path to the
.Xr psql 1
binary (default:
.Li psql ) .
.It Ar ssl_mode
SSL mode for the connection (default:
.Li prefer ) .
